---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="intro-container">
    <div class="intro-card">
      <h1 class="intro-title">原始 93 题测试</h1>
      <ul class="intro-list">
        <li>保持原始题库和交互方式（两项选择）。</li>
        <li>预计耗时约 20~30 分钟。</li>
        <li>答案无对错，凭第一直觉选择即可。</li>
      </ul>
      <button class="intro-btn" id="start-btn-original">开始 93 题</button>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-card">
      <h1 class="intro-title">新版 100 题多维测评</h1>
      <ul class="intro-list">
        <li>共 100 道题，采用 1~5 分评分（非常不同意→非常同意）。</li>
        <li>题目顺序会随机打乱，每次测试体验不同。</li>
        <li>完成后将生成更丰富的 AI 个性分析。</li>
      </ul>
      <button class="intro-btn" id="start-btn-new">开始 100 题</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script type="module">
  document.getElementById('start-btn-original').addEventListener('click', () => {
    window.location.href = '/test?bank=original';
  });
  document.getElementById('start-btn-new').addEventListener('click', () => {
    window.location.href = '/test?bank=new';
  });
</script>

<style is:global>
.intro-container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.intro-card {
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 80px auto;
  padding: 32px 24px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(74,108,247,0.10);
  font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  text-align: center;
}
.intro-title {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  color: #333;
}
.intro-list {
  text-align: left;
  margin: 0 auto 24px auto;
  padding-left: 1.2em;
  color: #555;
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.intro-list li {
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.intro-btn {
  background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #4a6cf7 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
  border: none;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 12px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.intro-btn:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(74,108,247,0.18);
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .intro-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .intro-card {
    margin: 40px 4vw;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }
  .intro-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .intro-list {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .intro-btn {
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 10px 0;
  }
}
</style>